 <strong>Abbott Laboratories</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ABT\" title=\"Abbott Laboratories\">ABT</a></span>), whose <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ABT/earnings\">next earnings</a> call is about a month away, so the goal is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2024514092/image_2024514092.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745763-abbott-laboratories-a-future-driven-pharma-brand-with-a-robust-pipeline", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 12:27:28", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745766", "title": "Fed Outlook 2025: Key Insights For Fixed Income Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Going to 2025. Woman hitchhiking alone and holding a cardboard sign\" data-id=\"2170334316\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Karen Veraa-Perry, CFA</em></p> <h2>What's The Outlook For Fed Policy In 2025?</h2> <p>At its final meeting of 2024, the Federal Reserve cut interest rates by 25 basis points; the Fed has now cut rates by 100 basis points</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170334316/image_2170334316.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745766-fed-outlook-2025-key-insights-for-fixed-income-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 12:22:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745762", "title": "Carnival: Smooth Sailing Ahead", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman sitting on a boat and splashing on the water\" data-id=\"1255512267\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Constantinis/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>I am bullish on Carnival Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CCL\" title=\"Carnival Corporation &amp; plc\">CCL</a></span>) after <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19954037-carnival-corporation-and-plc-outperforms-fourth-quarter-guidance-reports-record-full-year\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19954037-carnival-corporation-and-plc-outperforms-fourth-quarter-guidance-reports-record-full-year\" target=\"_blank\">Q3 FY24 earnings release</a> yesterday on Dec 20 2024:</p> <ol> <li>Peak occupancy, higher pricing and increased onboard spend is leading to upgrades in the earnings outlook</li> <li>New ships can drive long term</li> </ol>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255512267/image_1255512267.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745762-carnival-smooth-sailing-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 12:14:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745759", "title": "Adobe: Will Text-To-Image Disrupt Adobe's Business Model?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1622087545/image_1622087545.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Artificial intelligence cpu is generating user requests, 3d rendering\" data-id=\"1622087545\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"15