": "4745764", "title": "Quality Control: A Global Perspective", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mechanic checking engine\" data-id=\"88620858\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sam Edwards/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Ryan Giannotto, CFA, Manager of Equity Index Research</em></p> <p>The quality factor has been a powerful driver of returns, not only in the US equity market but on a global basis as well. The challenge with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88620858/image_88620858.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745764-quality-control-global-perspective", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 11:50:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745755", "title": "BlackBerry Q3: The Cylance Aftermath", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cyber security and data protection on internet. Shield, secure access and encrypted connection protecting online information. Password protected system. Cybersecurity technology. Holographic icon.\" data-id=\"2153383852\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In today's market, even the worst performing companies can see their stocks soar at times. It's sometimes hard to find a name that is doing badly on both the business side as well as its equity. One name</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2153383852/image_2153383852.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745755-blackberry-q3-the-cylance-aftermath", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 11:26:14", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745761", "title": "Weekly Commentary: Deleveraging Doom Loop", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cardboard with word Deleveraging made by black alphabet stamps.\" data-id=\"1299744226\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1027px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ekaterina79</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Friday from Bloomberg: \"US Stocks Rise After 'Major Overreaction\" to Fed.\" There was certainly more to Wednesday's steep market selloff than a meaningfully more hawkish Fed statement and Powell press conference. Welcome to Washington dysfunction on steroids meets global market dysfunction.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299744226/image_1299744226.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745761-weekly-commentary-deleveraging-doom-loop", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 11:20:55", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745753", "title": "Safe Bulkers: Maintaining Buy Rating On This Quality Shipper", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ship in port\" data-id=\"139540669\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3072px\" height=\"2304px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395406